---
title: KMS Key Lifecycle States
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Enabled : CreateKey
    Enabled --> Disabled : DisableKey
    Disabled --> Enabled : EnableKey
    Enabled --> PendingDeletion : ScheduleKeyDeletion
    Disabled --> PendingDeletion : ScheduleKeyDeletion
    PendingDeletion --> Disabled : CancelKeyDeletion
    PendingDeletion --> [*] : Waiting period expires\n(7-30 days)\nKEY DESTROYED

    note right of PendingDeletion
        Cannot encrypt/decrypt
        Helps find dependencies
        7 days min, 30 days max
    end note

    note right of Disabled
        Cannot encrypt/decrypt
        Key material preserved
        Can re-enable anytime
    end note

    note right of Enabled
        Normal operations
        Encrypt/Decrypt/Sign
        Auto-rotation (if configured)
    end note
